data.description: $10,000  price reduction. , Location, Location! ! Just in time for the holiday season! Here's a wonderful opportunity to make this lovely  4 Bedroom, 2 Full Bath Rancher in Belair your home! This property has it ALL! Great room sizes, formal Living Room, eat-in kitchen.  PLUS an enormous finished basement for entertaining. The main level features hardwood flooring throughout, four bedrooms, and a spacious updated eat-in kitchen . The fully finished lower level offers a large living area,  a built-in bar/entertainment area, and a work shop. Find plenty of additional storage in the garage and laundry area . A basement walkout leads to a patio and private sunroom, and spacious backyard. Convenient to 95, 24 , shopping, restaurants and so much more.
